overview: Roque (Marcelo Valdez) returns looking after who once was his nanny to take her to live with him in Buenos Aires. But Nana (Eva Prado) has left. It's the story of two travels, that of Nana to her hometown in ruins and that of Roque through the memories of his childhood searching for something that could reveal where Nana has gone.
title: Nana (historia de un viaje)
